snippet.textDisplay:
I'm from South Africa. And I have seen the fear in small business owners eyes. I talk to a lot of them. And all I want to do is make them happy. I pour as much energy into each and every person I come across to bring peace and happiness. It's tiring but it is what is needed.
Small business owners are struggling. So to make them smile and laugh for those few moments is so important..... Because that will last longer Than you see with your eyes. While they are at home in lock down in panic, they will remember that moment and smile... That makes me happy because that means I did the best I could do.

You do the same. Thank you for everything you do. I appreciate it so much. You inspire me to build my own empire. I have massive visions for my future and where I want to be. And I have to fight to have what I want.... Like you have done. You have done everything you have had to do. I will do the same.

Much love and peace
Matt
